1
00:00:03,533 --> 00:00:05,330
<i>我要再看一眼.有人反对吗?</i>
<i>I wanna take another look.Anyone object?</i>

2
00:00:05,413 --> 00:00:07,131
<i>不不,看吧,请便</i>
<i>No,go ahead.Be my guest.</i>

3
00:00:09,813 --> 00:00:12,691
- 我从来没有见过那么多的钱 - 主啊
- I've never seen that much money. - Mercy.

4
00:00:13,133 --> 00:00:15,328
看看这些.真是太夸张了
Look at that.That is awesome.

5
00:00:15,413 --> 00:00:18,450
- 你觉得这里有多少? - 我不知道.几千吧
- How much do you think there is? - I don't know.Thousands.

6
00:00:18,533 --> 00:00:19,602
好了
All right.

7
00:00:20,893 --> 00:00:22,884
我还是觉得我们应该交给警察
I still say we should take it to the police.

8
00:00:22,973 --> 00:00:26,602
等等,好吗.听我把话说完,行不?我们中的一个拿着这
Hold on,all right.Just hear me out,okay?One of us holds it.

9
00:00:26,693 --> 00:00:28,604
我们保留,大概,我不知道,30天
We check in,say,I don't know,30 days...

10
00:00:28,693 --> 00:00:32,049
如果没有人来报告丢失,我们就三个人平分了
if nobody's reported it missing,then we split it between us.

11
00:00:33,933 --> 00:00:37,243
是啊.好吧,就这样
Yeah.All right.Okay.

12
00:00:37,733 --> 00:00:40,930
那么,谁来拿着?
So,who holds it?

13
00:00:43,053 --> 00:00:44,884
- 我不介意 - 不
- I wouldn't mind. - No.

14
00:00:45,253 --> 00:00:47,721
不,因为我都不认识你 我也不认识他
No,'cause I don't know you,and I don't know him.

15
00:00:47,813 --> 00:00:49,804
我怎么能够假定你们不会消失?
How am I supposed to know you won't disappear?

16
00:00:49,893 --> 00:00:51,849
是啊,他说到重点了
Yeah,he has got a point.

17
00:00:55,013 --> 00:00:58,289
如果是我们在这里,他来照管呢?
What about if our man here,he looks after it?

18
00:00:58,373 --> 00:01:01,171
为了证明他不是个小偷,我并不是说你就是...
But to prove he's not a thief,I'm not saying that you are...

19
00:01:01,253 --> 00:01:02,971
他可以去银行.这太聪明了
he goes to the bank.This is brilliant.

20
00:01:03,053 --> 00:01:04,202
取出...你有多少?
Take out...What you got?

21
00:01:04,293 --> 00:01:06,011
我的社保账户里面有6000镑
I've got 6,000 in the building society.

22
00:01:06,093 --> 00:01:09,802
你有6000镑,好,那就拿出来6000 给我们每人3000
You've got 6,000,okay.Takes out 6,000.Gives us 3,000 each.

23
00:01:09,893 --> 00:01:11,645
- 而我则拿着箱子 - 当然
- But I keep the case? - Obviously.

24
00:01:11,733 --> 00:01:13,052
我没什么问题
I ain't got a problem with that.

25
00:01:13,133 --> 00:01:17,012
如果一个月内你都没有听到任何事情 我们就回来,一起分这个钱
If you don't hear anything in a month,we'll come back.Split the money.

26
00:01:17,453 --> 00:01:19,728
- 好吧 - 是吧?好了,就这样吧
- Okay. - Yeah?Okay.Let's do it.

27
00:01:21,813 --> 00:01:24,043
伙计,我们要发财了 我都不能相信
Man,we're gonna be so rich.I can't believe it.

28
00:01:24,133 --> 00:01:26,647
今天早上我出来的时候,口袋里面就只有20镑
I came out this morning,I had 20 quid in my pocket.

29
00:01:26,733 --> 00:01:30,487
而现在,我就能分到25000镑的三分之一了
Now,I'm looking at a third share in 25,000.

30
00:01:30,573 --> 00:01:33,565
从天而降,碰巧就被我们找到了
It's like it just came out of the sky and we just found it there.

31
00:01:33,653 --> 00:01:35,689
天堂的礼物啊
Brought from heaven,or something.

32
00:01:37,893 --> 00:01:39,565
现在情况如何,Danny?
How's it going,Danny?

33
00:01:41,013 --> 00:01:43,163
- 什么? - 比分
- What? - The score.

34
00:01:43,773 --> 00:01:47,004
如果以1-10分来评判,你觉得有多少分?
How do you think it's going on a scale of 1 to 10?

35
00:01:47,373 --> 00:01:49,682
或许9分?
A nine maybe?

36
00:01:52,813 --> 00:01:54,246
9分左右
Nine-ish.

37
00:01:55,773 --> 00:01:58,333
- 没有吗? - 问你的问题
- No? - Ask your question.

38
00:01:59,773 --> 00:02:02,446
你怎么知道这个箱子里面有多少钱?
How do you know how much is in the case?

39
00:02:06,213 --> 00:02:07,851
我们还没有数吗?
We didn't count it yet?

40
00:02:11,093 --> 00:02:12,162
妈的
Shit.

41
