00:30:16,782 --> 00:30:18,977
少管和你无关的事
Keep your nose out of what doesn't concern you.

320
00:30:19,062 --> 00:30:20,893
好了,够了
Okay,that's enough.

321
00:30:21,062 --> 00:30:23,371
你要管好你的嘴,孩子
You want to watch your mouth,boy.

322
00:30:23,462 --> 00:30:26,852
对不起,Frank,Jeff只是很讨厌Joe
I'm sorry,Frank,Jeff's just wound up about Joe.

323
00:30:28,262 --> 00:30:31,095
好吧,好吧,不带他了
Okay,look.All right.He's out.

324
00:30:31,382 --> 00:30:33,373
那我要找其他人来帮他收尾
I'll get somebody else to cover his end.

325
00:30:33,462 --> 00:30:35,373
这里是Frank的办公室...
Now,this is Frank's office...

326
00:30:36,102 --> 00:30:38,218
还是要有些尊重的
a bit of respect wouldn't go amiss.

327
00:30:38,622 --> 00:30:41,375
- 你找到买主了吗? - 都会安排妥当的
- You found a buyer yet? - It's all in place.

328
00:30:41,462 --> 00:30:44,181
我们在15000镑的时候买进 等到60000的时候再出来
We buy in at 15,000,we get back 60,000.

329
00:30:44,582 --> 00:30:45,981
这就是电影的特殊之处
That's film extras.

330
00:30:46,302 --> 00:30:49,533
在所有的演员中介里面 他们试图对每个带有...
In all the casting agencies,they try and strike up an exclusive...

331
00:30:49,622 --> 00:30:51,340
强大预算的电影构造一个专有权
with any movie with a decent budget.

332
00:30:51,422 --> 00:30:53,572
这只是盛大安排中的一个小土豆...
It's small potatoes in the grand scheme of things...

333
00:30:53,662 --> 00:30:55,573
但是,嘿,每一点都是要计算的,不是吗?
but,hey,every little counts,right?

334
00:30:55,662 --> 00:30:57,095
除了我们刚失去了Joe
Except we just lost Joe.

335
00:30:57,182 --> 00:30:58,934
- 我说了,我会来操心的 - 怎么弄?
- I said,I'd take care of it. - How?

336
00:30:59,022 --> 00:31:01,616
这是桩现金交易.我们可是要在早餐的时候 和制片人见面的...
This is a cash deal.We meet the producer at breakfast...

337
00:31:01,702 --> 00:31:03,454
而那是银行还没有开门
before the banks open.

338
00:31:05,982 --> 00:31:07,335
你知道吗?
You know what?

339
00:31:07,502 --> 00:31:10,892
话说回来,我很高兴Joe已经出局了
Screw the deal,I'm glad Joe's out of it.

340
00:31:11,062 --> 00:31:14,498
这个家伙只对净赚的有兴趣 他什么都不懂
The guy's only interested in the bottom line.He's got no soul.

341
00:31:15,062 --> 00:31:18,259
你知道他最喜欢的电影是什么吗,Frank?<i>兰博</i>
You know what his favorite film is,Frank?<i>Rambo.</i>

342
00:31:18,342 --> 00:31:20,617
你怎么会和这样的家伙做生意的呢?
How are you gonna do business with a guy like that?

343
00:31:20,702 --> 00:31:24,456
- Bogart,Cagney,他们才是演电影的 - 你喜欢Cagney?
- Bogart,Cagney,now they made movies. - You like Cagney?

344
00:31:24,542 --> 00:31:26,453
他真是前无古人,后无来者
No one like him,before or since.

345
00:31:26,542 --> 00:31:27,941
- 最好的电影?<i>- 白热杀机</i>
- Best film?<i>- White Heat.</i>

346
00:31:28,022 --> 00:31:29,614
- "成了!妈!" - "世界之巅"
- "Made it,Ma." - "Top of the world."

347
00:31:29,702 --> 00:31:32,774
好电影,但不是他最好的 你知道他曾经是个舞者么?
Good film,but not his best.Do you know he was a dancer?

348
00:31:32,862 --> 00:31:34,978
- 在电影中穿插舞蹈? - 是的
- Came up through vaudeville? - That's right.

349
00:31:35,062 --> 00:31:37,496
电影中最好的歌者和舞者
Best song and dance man in the business.

350
00:31:37,742 --> 00:31:41,655
你们两个讨论结束的话,我们是否能回到手头的正事上来?
When you two have finished,can we get back to the job in hand?

351
00:31:42,222 --> 00:31:43,211
可以
Yeah.

352
00:31:45,822 --> 00:31:47,574
到底是什么问题?
So what is this deal exactly?

353
00:31:47,662 --> 00:31:50,574
是和制作人的问题,额外的合同
The deal is with the producer,for the extras contract.

354
00:31:50,662 --> 00:31:53,176
我们和他见面,付清他的钱 然后去片场...
We meet him,pay him off,then go to the set...

355
00:31:53,262 --> 00:31:55,492
从中介那家伙处去搜集钱
and collect from the guy from the agency.

356
00:31:55,582 --> 00:31:57,413
- 片场? - 是的
- A film set? - Yeah.

357
00:31:57,542 --> 00:32:01,217
问题是,就像Jeff说的,我们少了Joe 所以缺了5000镑
Trouble is,like Jeff says,we lost Joe so we're 5,000 light.

358
00:32:01,702 --> 00:32:03,852
我直说吧
Let me get this straight.

359
00:32:04,582 --> 00:32:06,857
你们给这个制片人15000镑...
You take this producer 15,000...

360
00:32:06,942 --> 00:32:10,651
然后就开车到片场去搜集60000镑?
then you drive over to the film set and collect 60,000?

361
00:32:10,982 --> 00:32:13,098
差不多就是这个意思
That's about the strength of it.

362
00:32:13,662 --> 00:32:16,699
如果我提供了你们缺的5000镑呢?
So what if I put up the 5,000 you're light?

363
00:32:16,782 --> 00:32:21,173
只要我提供了Joe这个家伙的份 那他的那份回报也就给我
So long as I pick up his share,this guy Joe's share,in return.

364
00:32:21,622 --> 00:32:23,578
- 没门 - 我没有在和你说
- No way. - I wasn't talking to you.

365
00:32:23,662 --> 00:32:25,061
你要让这个家伙硬挤进来吗?
You gonna let this guy muscle in?

366
00:32:25,142 --> 00:32:28,691
他所做的只是接管Joe的部分 那又有什么区别呢?
All he'd be doing is taking over Joe's share.What difference does it make?

367
00:32:28,782 --> 00:32:30,101
我都不认识这个家伙
I don't even know this guy.

368
00:32:30,182 --> 00:32:32,935
看在上帝的份上,这个猪头现在要给我们支票啊
For God's sake,the lame brain's gonna give us a check now.

369
00:32:33,022 --> 00:32:36,981
- Jeff,拜托,求你了.放松点 - 好吧
- Jeff,come on,please.Just relax. - All right.

370
00:32:37,342 --> 00:32:40,220
必须是要现金的,Frank.对不起
It does have to be cash,Frank.I'm sorry.

371
00:32:49,342 --> 00:32:50,616
你可不可以礼貌一些?
You gonna be polite?

372
00:32:50,702 --> 00:32:54,377
Frank帮我们脱离Joe呢 至少我们可以让他插进来吧
Frank helped us out with Joe.Cutting him in is the least we can do.

373
00:33:05,302 --> 00:33:06,291
谢谢,Frank
Thanks,Frank.

374
00:33:06,382 --> 00:33:10,375
就像我说的,我喜欢钱在我能看见的地方
Like I said,I like my money where I can see it.

375
00:33:11,262 --> 00:33:12,775
我和你们一起去
I'm coming with you.

376
00:33:14,222 --> 00:33:15,291
好的
All right.

377
00:34:07,702 --> 00:34:09,055
我要叫了
I'll call.

378
00:34:15,942 --> 00:34:17,341
3个7
Three sevens.

379
00:34:21,062 --> 00:34:22,051
同花
Flush.

380
00:34:28,542 --> 00:34:29,531
再来
Again.

381
00:34:50,702 --> 00:34:52,897
- Pete - 你倒是很及时嘛
- Pete. - You took your time.

382
00:34:52,982 --> 00:34:54,495
很高兴见到你
Nice to see you,too.

383
00:34:54,582 --> 00:34:58,131
钱在那个口开着的袋子里面 先把那个给Danny
The money's in the one with the flap open,so give that one to Danny first.

384
00:34:58,222 --> 00:34:59,974
- 什么时候? - 尽快吧
- How long? - Any minute now.

385
00:35:00,062 --> 00:35:01,734
记住不要让别人看见
Just be out of sight.

386
00:35:20,822 --> 00:35:23,973
我告诉过你了,Lucy 不拿开那条绳子我就走
I've told you,Lucy,either the line goes or I do.

387
00:35:24,462 --> 00:35:26,737
哦,耶酥基督,去告诉他们!
Well,Jesus Christ!Go and tell them.

388
00:35:27,382 --> 00:35:29,532
- Jenny亲爱的 - Jason
- Jenny baby. - Jason.

389
00:35:29,782 --> 00:35:30,897
怎么样了?
How's it going?

390
00:35:30,982 --> 00:35:33,416
导演是个蠢蛋 你能帮我开了他吗?
The director's a moron.Can't you fire him for me?

391
00:35:33,502 --> 00:35:36,380
亲爱的,我可以.但他会让我先滚蛋
Baby,I could,but he'd sue my ass off.

392
00:35:36,742 --> 00:35:39,893
这是我的一个很好的朋友,这是Frank Gorley
This is a very good friend of mine.This is Frank Gorley.

393
00:35:40,062 --> 00:35:41,973
- 很高兴见到你,Frank - 你好?
- Glad to meet you,Frank. - How do you do?

394
00:35:42,062 --> 00:35:44,781
好了,来吧,现在,回去工作 时间就是金钱
Okay,come on,now.Back to work.Time is money.

395
00:35:44,982 --> 00:35:46,859
他真是个苛刻的老板
He's such a slave driver.

396
00:35:48,982 --> 00:35:51,177
- 那是Jenny Cole? - 你认识她?
- That's Jenny Cole? - You know her?

397
00:35:51,262 --> 00:35:54,459
- 我今天早上看到她的新闻 - 她会成为巨星的
- I was reading about her this morning. - She's gonna be huge.

398
00:35:54,542 --> 00:35:56,772
他们把她称为奥黛丽・赫本第二
They're calling her the new Audrey Hepburn.

399
00:35:56,862 --> 00:35:58,932
- Jason - 你好吗?
- Jason. - How you doing?

400
00:35:59,262 --> 00:36:00,900
不错.交易还算数?
Okay.We still on?

401
00:36:00,982 --> 00:36:02,131
已经搞定了
It's a done deal.

402
00:36:02,222 --> 00:36:05,897
很好,我有200个超级崇拜的小明星 真等着点头呢,拿着
Great,I've got 200 wannabe starlets waiting for the nod,here.

403
00:36:06,262 --> 00:36:09,299
- 你们要来帮我选吗? - 不,我们委托你了,好吗?
- You fellas wanna help me pick? - No,we'll leave that,all right?

404
00:36:09,382 --> 00:36:12,180
你是准备说上一整天还是就把我的钱给我?
You gonna talk all day or you gonna give me my money?

405
00:36:13,942 --> 00:36:16,695
就像他说的,分成3份了
Split three ways,just like he said.

406
00:36:16,782 --> 00:36:18,500
漂亮
That's beautiful.

407
00:36:21,422 --> 00:36:26,098
20,000.一个半小时的回馈,不错吧
20,000.Not a bad return for half an hour,is it?

408
00:36:28,182 --> 00:36:31,618
- 看起来Joe的损失是我的获利嘛 - 我想是的
- Looks like Joe's loss is my gain. - I guess so.

409
00:36:34,302 --> 00:36:35,770
既然我们都到了这里
While we're here,

410
00:36:35,771 --> 00:36:38,853
何不逛逛这个片场,看看是如何拍电影的呢?
any chance of walking around the set,watching a bit of filming?

411
00:36:41,182 --> 00:36:44,413
Frank,我要回去了.要去摆平Joe
Frank,I gotta get back.Square things up with Joe.

412
00:36:45,062 --> 00:36:46,973
我以为Joe已经不再参与了呢
I thought Joe was out of the picture.

413
00:36:47,062 --> 00:36:49,132
他还在里面,在做笔大生意
He is for this but not the big one.

414
00:36:49,422 --> 00:36:51,982
- 大生意? - 闭嘴,Jason
- Big one? - Shut your mouth,Jason.

415
00:36:52,542 --> 00:36:54,976
- 我说什么了吗? - 上车吧
- Did I say anything? - Just get in the car.

416
00:36:59,022 --> 00:37:02,173
有谁问起我的话,就告诉他们我5分钟之前离开了
Anybody asks for me,tell them I left five minutes ago.

417
00:37:31,102 --> 00:37:32,774
我的4000镑在哪里?
So where's my 4,000?

418
00:37:33,062 --> 00:37:34,575
我们送出去了
We just gave it away.

419
00:37:38,982 --> 00:37:40,051
嗨,Eddie
Hi,Eddie.

420
00:37:40,302 --> 00:37:42,896
- 你们就把我的钱送出去了? - 是的
- Did you just give my money away? - It's all right.

421
00:37:43,342 --> 00:37:46,334
- 是个诱饵 - 诱饵?
- It was bait. - Bait?

422
00:37:47,862 --> 00:37:50,137
我们一切还顺利吧?
So did we get the green light?

423
00:37:51,342 --> 00:37:53,219
我们今晚会和他摊牌
We tell him the tale tonight.

424
00:38:04,222 --> 00:38:06,611
- 他来了.Frank.你好吧? - 很好
- Here he is.Frank.How are you doing? - Okay.

425
00:38:06,702 --> 00:38:08,454
- 你还记得Jenny吗? - 当然
- You remember Jenny? - Of course.

426
00:38:08,542 --> 00:38:11,215
她今天拍晚了.想要一些休息和放松
She wrapped late today.She wants a little bit of R and R.

427
00:38:11,302 --> 00:38:13,372
不好意思.你是Jennifer Cole?
Excuse me.Are you Jennifer Cole?

428
00:38:15,342 --> 00:38:16,775
你有笔吗?
Have you got a pen?

429
00:38:21,302 --> 00:38:22,576
谢谢
Thank you.

430
00:38:22,782 --> 00:38:26,377
你能在Jen玩牌的时候找个人看着她吗?
Can you get someone to watch over Jen while she plays the tables?

431
00:38:26,582 --> 00:38:27,651
没问题
No problem.

432
00:38:29,862 --> 00:38:31,898
不要让Cole小姐受到打扰
See Miss Cole isn't bothered.

433
00:38:32,182 --> 00:38:34,457
- 好好玩吧 - 谢谢,Frank
- Go have fun. - Thank you,Frank.

434
00:38:36,702 --> 00:38:39,216
- 我们能喝一杯吗? - 当然
- Can we get a drink? - Yeah.

435
00:38:39,662 --> 00:38:41,459
Joe怎么样了?
How did it go with Joe?

436
00:38:42,182 --> 00:38:44,935
- 这个家伙是个蠢蛋 - 我6个月前就告诉你了
- The guy's a fruit loop. - I told you that six months ago.

437
00:38:45,022 --> 00:38:47,138
真是羞愧啊,我还有些喜欢他呢,你知道吗?
It's a shame,I kind of liked him,you know?

438
00:38:47,222 --> 00:38:49,531
- 但这可是在做买卖 - 是是是
- But this is business. - Yeah.

439
00:38:49,862 --> 00:38:52,979
那那个大生意是什么东西?
So what about the big one?

440
00:38:55,462 --> 00:38:59,091
- 你之前有提起过 - Jeff?
- You mentioned it earlier. - Jeff?

441
00:39:00,542 --> 00:39:03,261
好了,Frank,坐下
Okay,Frank,sit down.

442
00:39:03,342 --> 00:39:04,331
告诉他吧
Tell him.

443
00:39:06,462 --> 00:39:11,013
我们准备要制作部电影 低成本的.大概是5百万英镑
We're gonna make a movie.Kind of low budget.Say about 5,000,000.

444
00:39:12,662 --> 00:39:14,857
而Jenny觉得现在是她转型的时候...
Jenny thinks it's her big break in the States...

445
00:39:14,942 --> 00:39:18,571
但我们真正想在亚洲赚钱
but where we're really gonna make our money is in Asia.

446
00:39:19,222 --> 00:39:20,211
亚洲?
Asia?

447
00:39:20,662 --> 00:39:24,098
- 我能坦白讲吗,Frank? - 请
- Can I be frank,Frank? - Please.

448
00:39:24,262 --> 00:39:27,174
在其他的人正盯着家庭市场的时候...
While everyone else is looking at the home market...

449
00:39:27,702 --> 00:39:31,172
我们先把影片直接卖给亚洲
we sell the video rights to Asia up front.

450
00:39:32,622 --> 00:39:34,499
我们可以直接给出价钱
We can virtually name our price.

451
00:39:34,582 --> 00:39:37,972
那样我们可以不费吹灰之力就能赚到1千万英镑
I figure we're gonna get 10 million without breaking a sweat.

452
00:39:39,222 --> 00:39:44,012
- 她同意那么做? - 她昨天已经签订合同了
- And she's agreed to do it? - She signed the contract yesterday.

453
00:39:44,542 --> 00:39:46,021
Joe在里面还是不在?
So is Joe in or out?

454
00:39:46,262 --> 00:39:49,220
他还想进来,但你知道这些乌合之众是如何的
He still wants in,but you know what these Mob guys are like.

455
00:39:49,302 --> 00:39:50,781
他们还是有点钱的
They're a liability.

456
00:39:50,982 --> 00:39:52,574
这是净赚的,Frank:
Bottom line is,Frank:

457
00:39:52,662 --> 00:39:56,098
如果你想分一羹的话 我可以帮你
If you want a slice of the cake,I can make it happen.

458
00:39:57,542 --> 00:39:59,533
我们要投入多少钱?
How much are we talking about?

459
00:40:00,662 --> 00:40:03,699
你要投入的跟我和Jeff一样多
It's gonna be the same as me and Jeff are in for.

460
00:40:03,942 --> 00:40:05,819
20万左右吧
That's 200 big ones.

461
00:40:06,702 --> 00:40:08,181
20万英镑?
200,000?

462
00:40:08,942 --> 00:40:10,660
而保证是...
With a guarantee...

463
00:40:10,742 --> 00:40:14,417
你可以在3个月之内收回双倍的回馈
that you're gonna get double your money back in three months.

464
00:40:18,742 --> 00:40:20,937
不,我觉得我还是不要了
No,I think I'll pass.

465
00:40:21,902 --> 00:40:22,891
什么?
What?

466
00:40:23,262 --> 00:40:26,493
我最多出到15000镑,再多我就退出了
I'm 15,000 up.I think I'll quit while I'm ahead.

467
00:40:26,582 --> 00:40:29,858
- 如果我们... - 我们可以找到别人的
- What if we... - We can find someone else.

468
00:40:30,142 --> 00:40:32,178
这不是问题,好吗?
It's not a problem,okay?

469
00:40:33,902 --> 00:40:36,052
- 我们刚才要的酒呢? - 当然
- How about that drink? - Sure.

470
00:40:49,982 --> 00:40:51,893
你要认识到一件事情,Dan
You've got to pick it up,Dan.

471
00:40:52,182 --> 00:40:53,934
你在跟这个家伙谈钱
You're talking to this guy about money.

472
00:40:54,022 --> 00:40:56,661
他被钱所包围,而不是被钱困扰
He's surrounded by money,he's not fazed by it.

473
00:40:56,742 --> 00:40:59,336
你给他的是一些他已经有的东西
You're offering him something he's already got.

474
00:40:59,422 --> 00:41:02,220
你要想想什么能带给我们比钱更多的
You've gotta think about what brought us this far.

475
00:41:02,742 --> 00:41:07,258
你能不能给他一些他从其他地方 所得不到的东西?
What can you give him that he can't get anywhere else?

476
00:41:08,102 --> 00:41:11,981
不要跟他的头脑说话,要跟他的心去说 是情感而不是理智
Don't talk to his head,talk to his heart.Emotion not reason.

477
00:41:15,742 --> 00:41:16,857
想想吧
Think.

